<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>163</hymn_number>
<title>JESUH A TUM THAN LAI CH163</title>
<key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khuadeinak arfi deirel chuah caan ah siseh, Khuamuihnak ka in ni a
 chuah lioah siseh, Jesuh lianhnak he hi vawlei ah a tum lai, A zummi a
 khawmh hna lai.

[C1]
   Maw ka Pathian, zeitikah dah lawmhnak hla ka sak lai? Hal-le-lu-jah!
   Jesuh tum than, Hal-le-lu-jah! Amen! Hal-le-lu-jah! Amen!

[V2]
 Chun ling ah siseh, zanlei sang zongah siseh, Zantim khuamui, mui
 cirik caan khum-ah siseh, Pathian lianhngannak in Jesuh kha a tum lai, A
 zummi a khawmh hna lai.

[C2]
   Maw ka Pathian, zeitikah dah lawmhnak hla ka sak lai? Hal-le-lu-jah!
   Jesuh tum than, Hal-le-lu-jah! Amen! Hal-le-lu-jah! Amen!

[V3]
 Mithiangmi hna le, vancungmi cu hmunkhat ah, An thawng a thang lai,
 vancung in a tum lioah, Pathian lianhnak kha, A velchum ah a tlang lai, A
 zummi a khawmh hna lai.

[C3]
   Maw ka Pathian, zeitikah dah lawmhnak hla ka sak lai? Hal-le-lu-jah!
   Jesuh tum than, Hal-le-lu-jah! Amen! Hal-le-lu-jah! Amen!

[V4]
 Kan lung tum bik cu, phak kan duh ko thih loin, Ngaihchiat, tahhram,
 zawt, retheih, sifah luatnak in, Pathian nih minmei in a kan kaipi ahcun,
 Zeitluk in kan i lawmh lai.

[C4]
   Maw ka Pathian, zeitikah dah lawmhnak hla ka sak lai? Hal-le-lu-jah!
   Jesuh tum than, Hal-le-lu-jah! Amen! Hal-le-lu-jah! Amen!</lyrics>
</song>